========== Passives =========
Condition Immunities: blinded, deafened, frightened
False Appearance: While the shrieker remains motionless, it is indistinguishable from an ordinary fungus
Shriek: As a reaction, when bright light or a creature is within 30 ft of the shrieker, it emits a shriek audible within 300 ft of it. The shrieker continues to shriek until the disturbance moves out of range and for 1d4 of the shrieker's turns afterward
